 - [Programming in Apache Qpid](http://qpid.apache.org/books/${version}/Programming-In-Apache-Qpid/html/index.html) ([PDF](http://qpid.apache.org/books/${version}/Programming-In-Apache-Qpid/pdf/Programming-In-Apache-Qpid.pdf))
 - [Guide to the C++ broker](http://qpid.apache.org/books/${version}/AMQP-Messaging-Broker-CPP-Book/html/index.html) ([PDF](http://qpid.apache.org/books/${version}/AMQP-Messaging-Broker-CPP-Book/pdf/AMQP-Messaging-Broker-CPP-Book.pdf))
 - [Guide to the Java broker](http://qpid.apache.org/books/${version}/AMQP-Messaging-Broker-Java-Book/html/index.html) ([PDF](http://qpid.apache.org/books/${version}/AMQP-Messaging-Broker-Java-Book/pdf/AMQP-Messaging-Broker-Java-Book.pdf))
 - [Installing and Using Qpid Java](https://cwiki.apache.org/qpid/getting-started-guide.html)
