 - [Installing Qpid Python](http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/qpid/tags/${version}/qpid/python/README.txt)
 - [Installing Qpid WCF](http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/qpid/tags/${version}/qpid/wcf/ReadMe.txt)
 - [C++ Messaging API reference](http://qpid.apache.org/apis/${version}/cpp/html/index.html) ([qpid-cpp-doxygen-${version}.html.tar.gz](http://qpid.apache.org/apis/${version}/cpp/qpid-cpp-doxygen-${version}.html.tar.gz))
 - [Python Messaging API reference](http://qpid.apache.org/apis/${version}/python/html/index.html) ([qpid-python-epydoc-${version}.html.tar.gz](http://qpid.apache.org/apis/${version}/python/qpid-python-epydoc-${version}.html.tar.gz))

